etsysLicenseKeyMIB.name: etsysLicenseKeyMIB

revisions.description: Increased the size of the etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalString object.

Added the etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalTable to represent licensable features that are bound to specific physical subsystems. Obsoleted the etsysLicenseKeyTable since it can be represented in the etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalTable.
Added a new enumeration to the etsysLicenseKeyStatus object to indicate licenses that are valid but the system has not yet activated.
The initial version of this MIB module.

etsysLicenseKeyMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP enterprise MIBs under Enterasys Networks' enterprise OID pertaining to the configuration of license keys.

LicenseKeyStatus.name: LicenseKeyStatus
LicenseKeyStatus.description: This textual convention enumerates the possible status values for a given license key.

etsysLicenseKeyTable.name: etsysLicenseKeyTable
etsysLicenseKeyTable.description: This table contains license keys for optional features.

etsysLicenseKeyEntry.name: etsysLicenseKeyEntry
etsysLicenseKeyEntry.description: Information for a particular license key.

etsysLicenseKeyIndex.name: etsysLicenseKeyIndex
etsysLicenseKeyIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies each entry in this table. This value is only unique within a given managed device.

etsysLicenseKeyIdentifier.name: etsysLicenseKeyIdentifier
etsysLicenseKeyIdentifier.description: The unique OID for this licensable feature.

etsysLicenseKeyDescription.name: etsysLicenseKeyDescription
etsysLicenseKeyDescription.description: A textual description of this licensable feature.

etsysLicenseKeyString.name: etsysLicenseKeyString
etsysLicenseKeyString.description: The textual license key for this feature that has been, or will be, entered by the end user.

etsysLicenseKeyStatus.name: etsysLicenseKeyStatus
etsysLicenseKeyStatus.description: The status of the license key for this feature.

etsysLicenseKeyStatusText.name: etsysLicenseKeyStatusText
etsysLicenseKeyStatusText.description: A textual description of the status of the license key for this feature.

etsysLicenseKeyLastModified.name: etsysLicenseKeyLastModified
etsysLicenseKeyLastModified.description: The local date and time at which the license key string, etsysLicenseKeyString, associated with this row was last modified. If this information is not available, or the license key string has not been modified, this object MUST return '00000000'H.

etsysLicenseKeyExpiration.name: etsysLicenseKeyExpiration
etsysLicenseKeyExpiration.description: The local date and time at which this license key will expire. Once the key has expired this object will indicate the local date and time when the key expired. If the key does not have an expiration period then this object MUST return '00000000'H.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalTable.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalTable
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalTable.description: This table contains license keys for optional features.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalEntry.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalEntry
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalEntry.description: An entry containing per physical component information for a particular license key. Only physical indexes that have unique licensable features are represented in this table. Such physical entities may include, but are not limited to, ports, slots in a chassis, or the chassis itself.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalIndex.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalIndex
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies each entry in this table. This value is only unique within a given managed device.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalIdentifier.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalIdentifier

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalDescription.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalDescription
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalDescription.description: A textual description of this licensable feature.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalString.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalString
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalString.description: The textual license key for this feature that has been, or will be, entered by the end user.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatus.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatus
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatus.description: The status of the license key for this feature.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatusText.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatusText
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalStatusText.description: A textual description of the status of the license key for this feature.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalLastModified.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalLastModified
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalLastModified.description: The local date and time at which the license key string, etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalString, associated with this row was last modified. If this information is not available, or the license key string has not been modified, this object MUST return '00000000'H.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalExpiration.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalExpiration
etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalExpiration.description: The local date and time at which this license key will expire. Once the key has expired this object will indicate the local date and time when the key expired. If the key does not have an expiration period then this object MUST return '00000000'H.

etsysLicenseKeyConfigurationGroup.name: etsysLicenseKeyConfigurationGroup
etsysLicenseKeyConfigurationGroup.description: A collection of objects for configuring license keys for optional features.

etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalConfigGroup.name: etsysLicenseKeyPhysicalConfigGroup
